{"kanda":6,"sarga":23,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"निमित्तानिनिमित्ताज्ञोदृष्टवालक्ष्मणपूर्वजः ।सौमित्रिंसम्परिष्वज्यइदंवचनमब्रवीत्","trans":"Perceiving the portents, Rama spoke these words embracing Saumithri who was aware of the portents.","words":[{"d":"निमित्तज्ञः","m":"one who is aware of portents"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणपूर्वजः","m":"Lakshmana's elder brother"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"perceiving"},{"d":"निमित्तानि","m":"portents"},{"d":"सौमित्रिम्","m":"to Saumithri"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"सम्परिष्वज्य","m":"embracing"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"निमित्तानिपरिगृह्योदकंशीतंवनानिफलवन्तिच ।बलौघंसंविभज्येमंव्यूह्यतिष्ठेमलक्ष्मण","trans":"\"Lakshmana Arrange a place in this forest where there is cool water and fruits for the battalions of the army, we shall remain (alert).\"","words":[{"d":"लक्ष्मण","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"शीतम्","m":"cool"},{"d":"उदकम्","m":"water"},{"d":"फलवन्ति","m":"fruit"},{"d":"वनानिच","m":"forests"},{"d":"परिगृह्य","m":"arranging"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"बलौघम्","m":"battalions of army"},{"d":"संविभज्य","m":"dividing"},{"d":"व्यूह्य","m":"the group"},{"d":"तिष्ठेम","m":"will remain."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"लोकक्षयकरंभीमंभयंपश्याम्युपस्थितम् ।निबर्हणंप्रवीराणामृक्षवानररक्षसाम्","trans":"\"Dreadful warriors, Bears, monkeys, and Rakshasas will be slain, and I foresee that which bodes destruction of people.\"","words":[{"d":"लोकक्षयकरम्","m":"that which bodes destruction to the people"},{"d":"भीमम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"प्रवीराणाम्","m":"for the warriors"},{"d":"ऋक्षवानररक्षसाम्","m":"Bears, monkeys and Rakshasas"},{"d":"निबर्हणम्","m":"will be slain"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"उपस्थितम्","m":"will happen"},{"d":"पश्यामि","m":"I foresee."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"वाताश्चकलुषावान्तिकम्पतेचवसुन्धराः ।पर्वताग्राणिवेपन्तेपतन्तिचमहीरुहाः","trans":"\"The wind is blowing mixed with dust, even the earth is cracking, mountain tops are shaking, and huge trees are breaking and falling down.\"","words":[{"d":"वाताः","m":"wind"},{"d":"कलुषाः","m":"mixed with dust is blowing"},{"d":"वान्ति","m":"cracking"},{"d":"वसुन्धराच","m":"even the earth"},{"d":"कम्पते","m":"shaking"},{"d":"पर्वताग्राणि","m":"mountain tops"},{"d":"वेपन्ते","m":"breaking"},{"d":"महीरुहाः","m":"huge trees"},{"d":"पतन्तिच","m":"and falling down."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"मेघाःक्रव्यादसङ्काशाःपरुषाःपरुषस्वनाः ।क्रूराःक्रूरंप्रवर्षन्तिमिश्रंशोणितबिन्दुभिः","trans":"\"Clouds resembling raw flesh in colour, are making harsh frightening sounds, and rain mixed with drops of blood.\"","words":[{"d":"क्रव्यादसङ्काशाः","m":"clouds resembling raw flesh in colour"},{"d":"परुषाः","m":"harsh"},{"d":"परुषस्वनाः","m":"in harsh tone"},{"d":"क्रूराः","m":"cruel"},{"d":"मेघाः","m":"clouds"},{"d":"क्रूरम्","m":"frightening"},{"d":"शोणितबिन्दुभिः","m":"even drops of blood"},{"d":"मिश्रम्","m":"mixed"},{"d":"प्रवर्षन्ति","m":"raining."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"रक्तचन्दनसङ्काशासन्ध्यापरमदारुणा ।ज्वलतःप्रपतत्येतदादित्यादग्निमण्डलम्","trans":"\"The twilight in red sandal colour is very frightening. The Sun is blazing, raining masses of fire in variegated colours.\"","words":[{"d":"रक्तचन्दनसङ्काशा","m":"like red sandal"},{"d":"सन्ध्या","m":"twilight"},{"d":"परमदारुणा","m":"very frightening"},{"d":"ज्वलतः","m":"blazing"},{"d":"आदित्यात्","m":"from the Sun"},{"d":"एतत","m":"of variegated colours"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"दीनादीनस्वराःक्रूरास्सर्वतोमृगपक्षिणः ।प्रत्यादित्यंविनर्धन्तिजनयन्तोमहाद्भयम्","trans":"\"The wild animals all over have a piteous look and wailing in low tone standing opposite the Sun is indicating fear.\"","words":[{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all over"},{"d":"क्रूराःमृगाः","m":"wild animals"},{"d":"दीनाः","m":"pathetic"},{"d":"दीनस्वराः","m":"wailing in low tone"},{"d":"महात्","m":"great"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"जनयन्तः","m":"producing"},{"d":"प्रत्यादित्य","m":"opposite the Sun"},{"d":"विनर्धन्ति","m":"indicating."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"रजन्यामप्रकाशस्तुसन्तापयतिचन्द्रमाः ।कृष्णरक्तांशुपर्यन्तोलोकक्षयइवोदितः","trans":"\"The moon devoid of glow even in the night is like the Sun with black rays around and red aura behind (the black).\"","words":[{"d":"लोकक्षये","m":"at the time of dissolution of the universe"},{"d":"उदितइव","m":"like the Sun"},{"d":"कृष्णरक्तांशपर्यन्तः","m":"with black rays around and red rays behind"},{"d":"चन्द्रमाः","m":"moon"},{"d":"रजन्याम्","m":"in the night"},{"d":"अप्रकाशः","m":"devoid of glow"},{"d":"सन्तापयति","m":"causing sorrow."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"ह्रस्वोरूक्षोऽप्रशस्तश्चपरिवेषस्सुलोहितः ।आदित्येविमलेनीलंलक्ष्मलक्ष्मणदृश्यते","trans":"\"Lakshmana the white Sun is appearing in copper colour around with black colour in the centre which had not been seen before. It is small and dreary.\"","words":[{"d":"लक्ष्मण","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"विमले","m":"white"},{"d":"आदित्ये","m":"Sun"},{"d":"ह्रस्वः","m":"becoming small"},{"d":"रूक्षः","m":"dreary"},{"d":"अप्रशस्तः","m":"that which had not been seen before"},{"d":"लोहितः","m":"copper coloured"},{"d":"परिवेषः","m":"around"},{"d":"नीलम्","m":"black"},{"d":"लक्ष्म","m":"in the centre"},{"d":"दृश्यते","m":"appears."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"रजसामहताचापिनक्षत्राणिहतानिच ।युगान्तमिवलोकानांपश्यशंसन्तीवलक्ष्मण","trans":"\"Lakshmana the stars devoid of brightness are indicating as though it is the time of dissolution of the universe?\"","words":[{"d":"लक्ष्मण","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"रजसा","m":"brightness"},{"d":"हतानि","m":"devoid"},{"d":"नक्षत्राणि","m":"the stars"},{"d":"लोकानाम्","m":"in the worlds"},{"d":"युगान्तम्","m":"end of universe at the time of dissolution"},{"d":"शंसन्तीव","m":"as if indicating"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"appears."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"काकाश्श्येनास्तथानीचागृध्राःपरिपतन्तिच ।शिवाश्चाप्यशिवान्नादान्नदन्तिसुमहाभयान्","trans":"\"The crows, hawks and eagles are falling down like small animals. Also, the jackals are creating fear by making howls.\"","words":[{"d":"काकाः","m":"crows"},{"d":"श्येनाः","m":"hawks"},{"d":"ततागृध्राः","m":"likewise eagles"},{"d":"नीचाः","m":"small"},{"d":"परिपतन्ति","m":"falling down"},{"d":"शिवाश्चापि","m":"also jackals"},{"d":"महाभयान्","m":"great fear"},{"d":"अशिवान्","m":"creating"},{"d":"नादान्","m":"howls"},{"d":"नदन्ति","m":"making."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"शैलैश्शूलैश्चखढगैश्चविसृष्टैःकपिराक्षसैः ।भविष्यत्यावृताभूमिर्मांसशोणितकर्दमा","trans":"\"The earth will turn into a mass of flesh and blood and will be covered by the mountains and tridents hurled by Vanaras and Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"कपिराक्षसैः","m":"Vanaras and Rakshasas"},{"d":"विसृष्टैः","m":"hurled"},{"d":"शैलैः","m":"mountains"},{"d":"शूलैश्च","m":"tridents"},{"d":"खढगैश्च","m":"with swords"},{"d":"मांसशोणितकर्दमा","m":"covered with flesh and blood"},{"d":"भूमिः","m":"earth"},{"d":"आवृता","m":"turning to"},{"d":"भविष्यति","m":"will become."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"क्षिप्रमद्यैवदुर्दर्षांपुरींरावणपालिताम् ।अभियामजनेनैवसर्वतोहरिभिर्ववृताः","trans":"All the Vanaras turning their direction will go immediately and now itself, swiftly to the city ruled by Ravana (said Rama to Lakshmana).","words":[{"d":"सर्वैः","m":"all"},{"d":"हरिभिः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"आवृताः","m":"turning direction"},{"d":"अद्यैव","m":"now itself"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"immediately"},{"d":"जवेनैव","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"रावणपालिताम्","m":"ruled by Ravana"},{"d":"पुरीम्","m":"city"},{"d":"अभियाम","m":"will go."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"इत्येवमुक्त्वाधर्मात्माधनवीसङ्ग्रामहर्षणः ।प्रतस्थेपुरतोरामोलङ्कामभिमुखोविभुः","trans":"Rama, the subduer of enemies in war, a celebrated one having spoken this way proceeded towards Lanka going in front wielding a bow.","words":[{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामधर्षणः","m":"one who subdues his enemies in war"},{"d":"विभुः","m":"a celebrated one"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"इत्येवम्","m":"in this way"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"धनवी","m":"wielding a bow"},{"d":"पुरतः","m":"in front"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"to Lanka"},{"d":"अभिमुखः","m":"towards"},{"d":"प्रतस्थे","m":"proceeded."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सविभीषणसुग्रीवास्ततस्तेवानरर्षभाः ।प्रतस्थिरेविनर्दन्तोनिश्चिताद्विषतांवधे","trans":"Then Vibheeshana, Sugriva and all bulls among Vanaras determined in the matter of slaying (the enemies) went roaring.","words":[{"d":"सविभीषण","m":"then Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सुग्रीवाः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"of them"},{"d":"वानरर्षभाः","m":"bulls among Vanaras"},{"d":"विनर्दन्तः","m":"roaring"},{"d":"निश्चितानाम्","m":"determined"},{"d":"द्विषताम्","m":"in the matter of"},{"d":"वधे","m":"slaying"},{"d":"प्रतस्थिरे","m":"went"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"राघवस्यप्रियार्थंतुसुतरांवीर्यशालिनाम् ।हरीणांकर्मचेष्टाभिस्तुतोषरघुपुङ्गवः","trans":"To make Rama happy, the excessively heroic Vanaras made monkey actions. Seeing that Rama felt happy. ।। इत्यार्षेवाल्मीकीयेश्रीमद्रामायणेआदिकाव्येयुद्धकाण्डेत्रयोविंशस्सर्गः ।। This is the end of the twenty third sarga of Yuddha Kanda of the first epic the holy Ramayana composed by sage Valmiki.","words":[{"d":"सुतरां","m":"excessively"},{"d":"वीर्यशालिनाम्","m":"heroes"},{"d":"हरीणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"to Rama"},{"d":"प्रियार्थम्","m":"to make him happy"},{"d":"कर्मचेष्टाभिः","m":"actions"},{"d":"रघुपुङ्गवः","m":"the delight of Raghus"},{"d":"तुतोष","m":"saw and felt happy"}]}]}